<p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">新时代，新思想；共交流，促发展。为了加强与兄弟院校之间的合作与交流，全面提升我校校友工作与服务水平。</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">9</span></span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">月</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">8</span></span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">日</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">上</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">午，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">校长助理、校友办主任夏光辉一行两人</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">前往江西应用科技学院交流</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">学习</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><br/></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20231011/1696986015493006868.jpg" title="1696986015493006868.jpg" alt="1696986015493006868.jpg" width="566.6" height="348.3" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 566.6px; height: 348.3px;"/><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family: 宋体;">江西应用科技学院</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">常务副校长、校友会会长干甜</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">代表学校向</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">来访同仁</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">表示热烈欢迎</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">并简单</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">介绍了</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">应科院</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">概况、发展和校友工作的开展情况</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。随后</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">双方围绕校友会组织建设、校友活动开展</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">等</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">相关工作</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">进行了</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">详细的交流</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">最后一致表示在以后工作中进一步加强交流与合作</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><br/></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20231011/1696986148570009703.jpg" title="1696986148570009703.jpg" alt="1696986148570009703.jpg" width="567" height="348" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 567px; height: 348px;"/><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp; &nbsp;座谈会后，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">在李园园副会长的陪同下</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">参</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">观</span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">江西应用科技学院</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">校友服务社和校史馆。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20231011/1696986260670091231.jpg" title="1696986260670091231.jpg" alt="1696986260670091231.jpg" width="567" height="348.3" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 567px; height: 348.3px;"/></p><p><br style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p><br/></p>